text: The Atjeh Greens (, PAH), also known as the Aceh Greens, is a regional political party in Aceh Indonesia that was founded in 2013. The Atjeh Greens has been established in seven districts and cities. According to Fahmi Cherly, the party seeks to be registered by the 2024 election. The Atjeh Greens has been supported by the Australian Greens as a part of the "Australian Political Parties for Democracy Program". ==References== ==External links== * Aceh Greens on Facebook Category:2013 establishments in Indonesia Category:Political parties established in 2012 Category:Political parties in Indonesia Category:Green political parties
